---
description: Workspace scope — macOS app only; web/ is out of scope
alwaysApply: true
---

This workspace is for the macOS mosaic app only.

- Do not edit, search, or reference `web/` unless the user explicitly asks.
- Do not run `bun`, `npm`, or Next.js commands under `web/`.
- For settings/schema/docs, use Swift sources and `docs/` — not `web/data/` or `web/messages/`.
- Localization changes belong in `Resources/Localizable.xcstrings`, not `web/messages/`.
- Skip `mosaic-backend` and other web-focused skills unless the user explicitly requests web/backend work.
